cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.SY 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with online nonlinear regression using recurrent neural networks. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of neural networks for learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.SD (Software Development) as it introduces a new algorithm for training RNNs, and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with the optimization of a system.
